channel.title: CVE Feed for B. Braun Melsungen AG -- OnlineSuite

item.title: CVE-2020-25174|2024-08-04T15:26:10.187Z -- b.%20braun%20melsungen%20ag -- onlinesuite
item.description: A DLL hijacking vulnerability in the B. Braun OnlineSuite Version AP 3.0 and earlier allows local attackers to execute code on the system as a high privileged user.

item.title: CVE-2020-25170|2024-08-04T15:26:09.606Z -- b.%20braun%20melsungen%20ag -- onlinesuite
item.description: An Excel Macro Injection vulnerability exists in the export feature in the B. Braun OnlineSuite Version AP 3.0 and earlier via multiple input fields that are mishandled in an Excel export.

item.title: CVE-2020-25172|2024-08-04T15:26:10.164Z -- b.%20braun%20melsungen%20ag -- onlinesuite
item.description: A relative path traversal attack in the B. Braun OnlineSuite Version AP 3.0 and earlier allows unauthenticated attackers to upload or download arbitrary files.
